A man who got Sh10,000 wedding support from an MP and the local CDF chairman claims he was ejected from a WhatsApp group and forced to refund the cash after taking on the legislator. 

It all started last November during preparations for Zack Kihenjo’s wedding in Nyeri County. 

Friends, relatives and well-wishers contributed money as he took an important step of his life. 



